3. **Ask for confirmation:**
   "Does this look good? Reply 'yes' to generate PDF, or tell me what to adjust."

### STEP 6: Generate PDF Automatically
After user confirms (says "yes", "looks good", "generate", etc.):

1. **Run generate.py via Shell tool:**
   ```bash
   cd /Users/dmytrolozynskyi/Documents/cv && python3 generate.py "[Job Title] at [Company]"
   ```

